<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Maw misual khamhtu, thihnak hmun
 Kalvary tlang, lei khi, ka hei cuan i
 Thlanriput le nilin chosang ah
 Uai riangmang in Vanbawi fa an kal pi.

[C1]
   A faktuk e, maw ka khamhtu Bawi
   Sualnak ngeilo, Vanbawi, hrinhniang cu
   Vailam ah, thir in, an khenh chih
   Kei sual ruangah, pardawh, bang an uaiter.

[V2]
 An khenhnak tung an putter i
 Rom ralkap nih fungin an tukchih
 Tuarkhawh tilo maw ka khamhtu Bawi
 Zei ruangah hme Vawilam tahnak a ing.

[V3]
 Luruh tlang cungin Bawipa nih
 Ka ti a hal tiah fakpi in a au
 A ral hna nih ti thur an pek i
 Chiatserhnak he a hnak ah fei in an chunh.</lyrics>
<key>G</key>
<title>MAW MISUAL KHAMHTU</title>
</song>